          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "This is a guided farm tour conducted throughout the day from 9:00am to 5:00pm daily. You will be taken on a guided tour of our farm lasting about 30 minutes, together with one of our farm guides. After the tour, the farm guide will conduct the introduction of VCO process, Enzyme process, and also a sample tasting of our very own signature fruit enzymes."
